<p>The Grand Prize consists of the exclusive opportunity to have Justin Bieber and Pencils of Promise Founder Adam Braun visit the middle school, secondary school or high school associated with the Grand Prize winner’s School Fundraising Page.  It is the Grand Prize winner’s obligation to obtain all necessary approvals and permissions to host such visit.  A condition of the Grand Prize is to grant permission for twenty-two (22) additional guests from this Promotion to attend Mr. Bieber’s visit.  Sponsor shall provide personal security for Mr. Bieber as necessary.  Should additional security be deemed necessary by the hosting school or town, it shall be the obligation of the Grand Prize winner to arrange for such measures to be taken. <strong>Exact date of visit to be determined by Sponsor in conjunction with the availability of Mr. Bieber.</strong> No cash value.</p>

<p>Each Weekly Prize consists of fifty (50) NOOK Simple Touch™ readers. The approximate retail value (“<strong>ARV</strong>”) of each Weekly Prize is $4,950.  The ARV of any prize is subject to price fluctuations in the consumer marketplace based on, among other things, any gap in time between the date the ARV is estimated for purposes of these Official Rules and the date the prize is awarded or redeemed.  If the actual purchase price of a prize is less than the ARV stated herein, the prize winner will NOT be entitled to a check, cash or other form of payment for the price difference.  
